This component provides several playlist locks. Each lock somehow filters/modifies playlist content.
Unlike autoplaylist, playlist lock allows you to modify content manually.
Provided locks:
1.Media Library changes tracker
-  Inserts new medial library items or removes deleted items.
2.Remove played
-  Automatically removes all instances of played song.

Building
In order to build, you will need to define some environment variables:
1. FB2KSDK must be pointing to the folder with foobar2000 SDK
3. BUILD_BIN_DIR will be used for project's output binary files (*.obj, etc)
4. BOOST must be pointing to the Boost library